    <h3 itemprop="headline">Polls open in Hungary in a key election that could unseat populist Prime Minister Orb&#225;n</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Hungarians are voting in a crucial election that could end populist Prime Minister Viktor Orbán's 16-year rule.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/12/polls-open-in-hungary-in-a-key-election-that-could-unseat-populist-prime-minister-orban/"  >(Justin Spike And Sam Mcneil, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
