    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">AI demand is so high, AWS customers are trying to buy out its entire capacity</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Amazon Web Services (AWS) chip business is “on fire,” Trainium offers better price-performance than Nvidia, and customers are so eager for AI compute capacity that they’re looking to buy up all that’s currently available.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/11/ai-demand-is-so-high-aws-customers-are-trying-to-buy-out-its-entire-capacity/"  >(Network World)</a>
    </p>
