    <h3 itemprop="headline">Here&#8217;s the meeting planning magic trick Google Calendar is missing</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Imagine you need to organize a meeting with people in Portland, Tokyo, and Sydney at the same time. Off the top of your head, what’s a time that’d actually work for everyone?
Don’t feel bad if you’re befuddled.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/11/heres-the-meeting-planning-magic-trick-google-calendar-is-missing/"  >(Justin Pot, Fast Company)</a>
