    <h3 itemprop="headline">As the iPod makes a comeback, here are some pointers to use it</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Remember the iPod? It’s making a quiet comeback.
Four years after Apple killed off its digital music player, secondhand sales are surging.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/09/one-tech-tip-a-new-generation-is-reviving-the-ipod-for-distraction-free-listening/"  >(Associated Press, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
