        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Is Mythos a blessing or a curse for cybersecurity? It depends on whom you ask</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The real question about Anthropic’s new Claude Mythos Preview AI model is whether it (and future models like it) will be more helpful to defensive cybersecurity or to hackers. To find out, Fast Company asked a number of cybersecurity pros.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/11/is-mythos-a-blessing-or-a-curse-for-cybersecurity-it-depends-who-you-ask/"  >(Mark Sullivan, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
