    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ichiro Suzuki's bronze statue loses its bat in an unveiling gone wrong at Mariners home ballpark</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Fans cried foul after the Seattle Mariners&apos; Ichiro Suzuki statue unveiling went wrong when the bronze figure&apos;s bat snapped during the tarp reveal.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/04/11/ichiro-suzukis-bronze-statue-loses-bat-unveiling-gone-wrong-mariners-home-ballpark/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 18:55:51 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 18:55:51 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="John Marshall, Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
