        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tillman Scholars make connections with each other and the community at annual Pat's Run</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Pat's Run began in 2004 as a way to honor the legacy of Pat Tillman, who walked away from an NFL career to serve his country in the wake of Sept. 11.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/04/11/tillman-scholars-make-connections-with-each-other-and-the-community-at-annual-pats-run/"  >(John Marshall, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 17:48:25 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 17:48:25 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
