      <img src="/static14/sports/2026/04/11/new-zealand-cyclist-kiaan-watts-suspended-punching-rival-rider-mid-race.webp" alt="New Zealand cyclist Kiaan Watts suspended after punching rival rider mid-race" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">New Zealand cyclist Kiaan Watts suspended after punching rival rider mid-race</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Cyclist Kiaan Watts was suspended 25 days after video captured him punching fellow rider Marijn Maas during the Ster van Zwolle race in the Netherlands last month.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/04/11/new-zealand-cyclist-kiaan-watts-suspended-punching-rival-rider-mid-race/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 19:02:34 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 19:02:34 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
