      <img src="/static14/sports/2026/04/11/nba-sees-168-players-sit-games-due-illness-injury-playoffs-approach.webp" alt="168 NBA players sit out games due to illness, injury as playoffs approach" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">168 NBA players sit out games due to illness, injury as playoffs approach</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A total of 168 NBA players sat out Friday night due to injury or illness as the regular season wraps up and stars rest ahead of the playoffs.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/04/11/nba-sees-168-players-sit-games-due-illness-injury-playoffs-approach/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 14:42:59 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 14:42:59 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
