        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The final day of the NBA regular season awaits, with a whole lot left to be decided</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Sunday is the final day of the NBA regular season, and exactly zero playoff and postseason matchups have been decided so far.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2026/04/11/the-final-day-of-the-nba-regular-season-awaits-with-a-whole-lot-left-to-be-decided/"  >(Tim Reynolds, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
