        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Politics Friday: High tensions at the Capitol as lawmakers tick down the to-do list</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      MPR News politics editor talks with two lawmakers about the remainder of the session, where it stands and what can get done.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/10/politics-friday-high-tensions-at-the-capitol-as-lawmakers-tick-down-the-todo-list/"  >(Brian Bakst and Matthew Alvarez, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 10 Apr 2026 12:29:48 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 10 Apr 2026 12:29:48 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Erica Zurek, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/10/minnesota-lawmakers-consider-expanding-ballpark-tax-to-fund-hcmc.webp" alt="Lawmakers consider expanding ballpark tax to fund HCMC" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Lawmakers consider expanding ballpark tax to fund HCMC</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A bipartisan proposal would expand a ballpark sales tax to support HCMC as the hospital warns of financial losses and reduced services.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/10/minnesota-lawmakers-consider-expanding-ballpark-tax-to-fund-hcmc/"  >(Erica Zurek, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Tue, 07 Apr 2026 14:37:59 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Tue, 07 Apr 2026 14:37:59 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Kirsti Marohn, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/07/brainerd-city-council-allows-homeless-shelter-to-operate-year-round.webp" alt="Brainerd allows homeless shelter to operate year round" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Brainerd allows homeless shelter to operate year round</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Last year, Brainerd City Council rejected a request to allow the Bridges on 7th warming shelter to operate through the summer, sparking a community debate. The shelter’s operators have worked to address concerns that it was attracting people from other communities.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/07/brainerd-city-council-allows-homeless-shelter-to-operate-year-round/"  >(Kirsti Marohn, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 04:05:59 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 04:05:59 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Matt Brown And Steve Peoples, Associated Press, Local 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/11/democrats-embrace-dei-as-american-values-at-national-action-network.webp" alt="Democrats embrace DEI as 'American values' at National Action Network" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Democrats embrace DEI as 'American values' at National Action Network</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Democratic presidential prospects touted the importance of diversity, equity and inclusion policies as a way to advance American values during the National Action Network conference in New York.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/11/democrats-embrace-dei-as-american-values-at-national-action-network/"  >(Matt Brown And Steve Peoples, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Wed, 08 Apr 2026 00:00:02 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Wed, 08 Apr 2026 00:00:02 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/08/trump-warns-a-whole-civilization-will-die-tonight-if-a-deal-with-iran-isnt-reached.webp" alt="U.S. and Iran agree to 2-week ceasefire" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">U.S. and Iran agree to 2-week ceasefire</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Iran’s Supreme National Security Council said it has accepted a two-week ceasefire and that it would negotiate with the United States in Islamabad beginning Friday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/08/trump-warns-a-whole-civilization-will-die-tonight-if-a-deal-with-iran-isnt-reached/"  >(The Associated Press, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 13:00:57 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 13:00:57 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/11/top-white-house-officials-encouraged-potential-bondi-replacement-make-case-trump-ag-job-sources.webp" alt="Top White House officials encouraged potential Bondi replacement to make case to Trump for AG job: Sources" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Top White House officials encouraged potential Bondi replacement to make case to Trump for AG job: Sources</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Acting Attorney General Todd Blanche made his pitch to President Trump just hours after Pam Bondi was dismissed on why he should be the next AG, sources told Fox News Digital.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/11/top-white-house-officials-encouraged-potential-bondi-replacement-make-case-trump-ag-job-sources/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 09 Apr 2026 14:32:40 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 09 Apr 2026 14:32:40 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, MPR News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/09/how-u-s-communities-have-responded-to-proposed-ice-detention-centers.webp" alt="How communities have responded to proposed ICE centers" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">How communities have responded to proposed ICE centers</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Homeland Security Secretary Markwayne Mullin is reviewing plans to convert warehouses into detention facilities for immigrants. Immigration officials have spent over $1 billion on 11 warehouses. But they have faced strong opposition.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/09/how-u-s-communities-have-responded-to-proposed-ice-detention-centers/"  >(The Associated Press, MPR News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
